<item>
            <title>[SPARK-29777] SparkR::cleanClosure aggressively removes a function required by user function</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-29777</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Following code block reproduces the issue:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
df &amp;lt;- createDataFrame(data.frame(x=1))
f1 &amp;lt;- function(x) x + 1
f2 &amp;lt;- function(x) f1(x) + 2

dapplyCollect(df, function(x) { f1(x); f2(x) })
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We get following error message:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
org.apache.spark.SparkException: R computation failed with
 Error in f1(x) : could not find function &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;f1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
Calls: compute -&amp;gt; computeFunc -&amp;gt; f2
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Compare that to this code block with succeeds:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
dapplyCollect(df, function(x) { f2(x) })
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
